  },
  {
    label: 'Incident response planning',
    body: 'Incident response planning ensures your business can recover quickly if a security breach occurs. We develop detailed response protocols, establish communication procedures, and conduct tabletop exercises so your team knows exactly what to do during a security incident.',
    icon: SVG_640('M296.5 69.2C311.4 62.3 328.6 62.3 343.5 69.2L562.1 170.2C570.6 174.1 576 182.6 576 192C576 201.4 570.6 209.9 562.1 213.8L343.5 314.8C328.6 321.7 311.4 321.7 296.5 314.8L77.9 213.8C69.4 209.8 64 201.3 64 192C64 182.7 69.4 174.1 77.9 170.2L296.5 69.2zM112.1 282.4L276.4 358.3C304.1 371.1 336 371.1 363.7 358.3L528 282.4L562.1 298.2C570.6 302.1 576 310.6 576 320C576 329.4 570.6 337.9 562.1 341.8L343.5 442.8C328.6 449.7 311.4 449.7 296.5 442.8L77.9 341.8C69.4 337.8 64 329.3 64 320C64 310.7 69.4 302.1 77.9 298.2L112 282.4zM77.9 426.2L112 410.4L276.3 486.3C304 499.1 335.9 499.1 363.6 486.3L527.9 410.4L562 426.2C570.5 430.1 575.9 438.6 575.9 448C575.9 457.4 570.5 465.9 562 469.8L343.4 570.8C328.5 577.7 311.3 577.7 296.4 570.8L77.9 469.8C69.4 465.8 64 457.3 64 448C64 438.7 69.4 430.1 77.9 426.2z'),
  },
  {
    label: 'SIEM services',
    body: 'SIEM services aggregate security data from across your IT environment into a single platform. This centralized view enables faster threat detection, streamlined security operations, and comprehensive visibility into potential security issues before they escalate.',
    icon: SVG_512('M256 0a64 64 0 1 1 0 128 64 64 0 1 1 0-128zm96 312c0 25-12.7 47-32 59.9l0 92.1c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48l-32 0c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48l0-92.1C172.7 359 160 337 160 312l0-40c0-53 43-96 96-96s96 43 96 96l0 40zM96 32a56 56 0 1 1 0 112 56 56 0 1 1 0-112zm16 240l0 32c0 32.5 12.1 62.1 32 84.7l0 75.3c0 1.2 0 2.5 .1 3.7-8.5 7.6-19.7 12.3-32.1 12.3l-32 0c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48l0-56.6C12.9 364.4 0 343.7 0 320l0-32c0-53 43-96 96-96 12.7 0 24.8 2.5 35.9 6.9-12.6 21.4-19.9 46.4-19.9 73.1zM368 464l0-75.3c19.9-22.5 32-52.2 32-84.7l0-32c0-26.7-7.3-51.6-19.9-73.1 11.1-4.5 23.2-6.9 35.9-6.9 53 0 96 43 96 96l0 32c0 23.7-12.9 44.4-32 55.4l0 56.6c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48l-32 0c-12.3 0-23.6-4.6-32.1-12.3 0-1.2 .1-2.5 .1-3.7zM416 32a56 56 0 1 1 0 112 56 56 0 1 1 0-112z'),
  },
  {
    label: 'Continuous monitoring & optimization',
    body: "Security isn't a one-time project. Our 24/7 SOC provides ongoing threat monitoring, while quarterly business reviews ensure your cybersecurity services in Los Angeles evolve with your growth and changing threat landscape.",
    icon: SVG_640('M415.9 274.5C428.1 271.2 440.9 277 446.4 288.3L465 325.9C475.3 327.3 485.4 330.1 494.9 334L529.9 310.7C540.4 303.7 554.3 305.1 563.2 314L582.4 333.2C591.3 342.1 592.7 356.1 585.7 366.5L562.4 401.4C564.3 406.1 566 411 567.4 416.1C568.8 421.2 569.7 426.2 570.4 431.3L608.1 449.9C619.4 455.5 625.2 468.3 621.9 480.4L614.9 506.6C611.6 518.7 600.3 526.9 587.7 526.1L545.7 523.4C539.4 531.5 532.1 539 523.8 545.4L526.5 587.3C527.3 599.9 519.1 611.3 507 614.5L480.8 621.5C468.6 624.8 455.9 619 450.3 607.7L431.7 570.1C421.4 568.7 411.3 565.9 401.8 562L366.8 585.3C356.3 592.3 342.4 590.9 333.5 582L314.3 562.8C305.4 553.9 304 540 311 529.5L334.3 494.5C332.4 489.8 330.7 484.9 329.3 479.8C327.9 474.7 327 469.6 326.3 464.6L288.6 446C277.3 440.4 271.6 427.6 274.8 415.5L281.8 389.3C285.1 377.2 296.4 369 309 369.8L350.9 372.5C357.2 364.4 364.5 356.9 372.8 350.5L370.1 308.7C369.3 296.1 377.5 284.7 389.6 281.5L415.8 274.5zM448.4 404C424.1 404 404.4 423.7 404.5 448.1C404.5 472.4 424.2 492 448.5 492C472.8 492 492.5 472.3 492.5 448C492.4 423.6 472.7 404 448.4 404z'),
  },
];

const serviceSchema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: 'Managed Cybersecurity Services',
  url: 'https://www.allsafeit.com/services/cybersecurity',
  serviceType: 'Cybersecurity',
  description: 'AllSafe IT provides enterprise-grade Managed Cybersecurity Services designed to defend your business against ransomware, phishing, and data breaches.',
  provider: { '@type': 'Organization', '@id': 'https://www.allsafeit.com#organization' },
};

const breadcrumbSchema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
  itemListElement: [
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://www.allsafeit.com' },
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Cybersecurity Services', item: 'https://www.allsafeit.com/services/cybersecurity' },
  ],
};
---

<Base
  title="Cybersecurity Services for Small Businesses | AllSafe IT"
  description="Protect your business with Cybersecurity Services for Small Businesses. Threat monitoring, EDR, email security, and proactive defense for small businesses."
  canonical="https://www.allsafeit.com/services/cybersecurity"
  schema={[serviceSchema, breadcrumbSchema]}
>
  <HeroService
    heading="Cybersecurity Services for Small Business"
    lead="Cybersecurity services for small business that protect your data, maintain compliance, and let your team focus on growth without the constant worry of evolving cyber threats."
    video={{
      poster: '/videos/2176-155747466_small_poster.0000000.jpg',
      mp4: '/videos/2176-155747466_small_mp4.mp4',
      webm: '/videos/2176-155747466_small_webm.webm',
    }}
  />

  <SectionIntro heading="Cybersecurity that lets you focus on winning">
    <p class="lead-text">Cyber threats continue to evolve, but your business shouldn't have to spend every day worrying about them. Cybersecurity services give small businesses enterprise-level protection without the enterprise-level cost or complexity. You get 24/7 threat monitoring, proactive defense, and rapid response from a dedicated team of security experts.</p>
    <p class="lead-text">This isn't about reacting to problems after they happen. It's about preventing them in the first place. With a managed cybersecurity services provider handling your security, your team stays productive, your data stays protected, and your business stays focused on what matters most: winning.</p>
    <p class="lead-text">Unlike one-time security audits or basic antivirus software, cybersecurity services for small business provide continuous protection. We follow frameworks like the NIST Cybersecurity Framework and Zero Trust architecture to ensure every access point, every device, and every user is verified and protected. Your security posture improves over time, adapting to new threats as they emerge.</p>
  </SectionIntro>

  <SplitContent
    heading="Layered security that works together"
    image="/images/businesstruly.webp"
    imageAlt="Security monitoring and threat protection for small business technology systems"
    bg="gradient"
  >
    <p class="body-text">Real cybersecurity solutions require multiple layers working in harmony. Think of it like protecting a building. You wouldn't rely on just a lock or just an alarm. You need both, plus cameras, access controls, and trained security personnel.</p>
    <p class="body-text">Our cybersecurity approach combines endpoint protection, network monitoring, email security, and security awareness training into a unified defense system. Each layer catches threats the others might miss. When they work together, potential threats get stopped before they can cause data loss or security breaches.</p>
    <p class="body-text">We use advanced tools like SIEM (Security Information and Event Management) for centralized threat monitoring and EDR (Endpoint Detection and Response) to protect devices wherever they are. Microsoft Defender integrates with your existing Microsoft 365 environment to provide seamless protection. This layered approach means cyber threats get detected and neutralized quickly, often before you even know they existed.</p>
    <p class="body-text">The difference between reactive and proactive security is simple. Reactive security fixes problems after they happen. Proactive security prevents them. Our security service focuses on the latter, keeping your business safe instead of just cleaning up after attacks.</p>
  </SplitContent>

  <ServiceCardList
    heading="Core Managed Cybersecurity Services"
    lead="Every small business needs a solid foundation of cybersecurity services to protect against modern threats. We've built our core services around the most critical security needs facing businesses today."
    items={coreServices}
  />

  <WhyChooseAccordion
    heading="Additional Cybersecurity Services your business might need"
    intro="Beyond core protections, some businesses benefit from additional security layers depending on their industry, compliance requirements, or specific risk profile."
    items={additionalServices}
    image="/images/personalized-it-support.jpg"
    imageAlt="Cybersecurity services helping small businesses prevent cyber attacks"
  />

  <SplitContent
    heading="Compliance made manageable"
    image="/images/managementservice.avif"
    imageAlt="Cybersecurity services for small business protecting networks, systems, and data"
  >
    <p class="body-text">Meeting compliance requirements doesn't have to be overwhelming. Our cybersecurity compliance services align your security controls with industry standards and regulatory frameworks.</p>
    <p class="body-text">Whether you need HIPAA compliance for healthcare data, PCI-DSS for payment card processing, or SOC 2 for customer trust, we map your security measures to the required controls. We follow established frameworks like ISO 27001 and the NIST Cybersecurity Framework to ensure comprehensive coverage.</p>
    <p class="body-text">Ongoing compliance is different from a one-time cybersecurity audit. We maintain documentation, conduct regular security assessments, and update controls as regulations evolve. When audit time comes, you're ready with organized evidence and documented procedures that demonstrate your compliance posture.</p>
    <p class="body-text">Our cybersecurity audit services provide independent verification that your controls are working as intended. Regular assessments identify gaps before auditors do, giving you time to remediate issues and maintain continuous compliance without surprises.</p>
  </SplitContent>

  <SplitContent
    heading="How AllSafe manages your security"
    image="/images/ITsupportworking.avif"
    imageAlt="IT security specialist monitoring threats for a small business environment"
    imageRight
    bg="gradient"
  >
    <p class="body-text">Our managed cybersecurity approach combines advanced technology with expert human oversight. Security operations run 24/7 with continuous threat monitoring through our SIEM platform. When potential threats are detected, our security analysts investigate and respond immediately.</p>
    <p class="body-text">We don't just react to alerts. Proactive threat detection uses threat intelligence feeds and behavioral analysis to identify suspicious activity before it becomes a breach. Regular security assessments help us understand your evolving risk profile and adjust protections accordingly.</p>
    <p class="body-text">Your security team includes dedicated security experts who know your environment, your business, and your specific needs. We handle everything from configuring security tools to investigating incidents to providing strategic cybersecurity consulting services. You get enterprise-level security expertise without the cost of building an in-house team.</p>
    <p class="body-text">Detection and response capabilities improve continuously. We track emerging threats, update defenses, and refine our response capabilities based on the latest threat intelligence. Your security gets stronger over time, not weaker.</p>
  </SplitContent>

  <SplitContent
    heading="Trusted Cybersecurity Services across Industries"
    image="/images/allsafe-employee-1.avif"
    imageAlt="Small business systems protected with professional cybersecurity services"
  >
    <p class="body-text">We've helped businesses across industries strengthen their security and maintain compliance. Healthcare organizations rely on us to maintain HIPAA compliance while protecting patient data. Retail businesses trust our PCI-DSS expertise to secure payment processing. Manufacturing companies depend on our protection for operational technology and intellectual property.</p>
    <p class="body-text">From construction firms protecting project data to hospitality businesses securing customer information, nonprofits safeguarding donor records to entertainment companies defending creative assets, we understand industry-specific security challenges. Our cybersecurity services adapt to your unique needs.</p>
  </SplitContent>

  <LocationCards heading="Cybersecurity Support Across Southern California" />

  <FaqSection faqs={CYBERSECURITY_FAQS} heading="Frequently Asked Questions" />

  <ContactSection
    heading="Partner with security experts who want you to win"
    body="Stop worrying about the next cyber threat. Let our security experts handle protection while you focus on growing your business."
  />
</Base>
